        P2["⚙️ Processing<br/>Apache Spark 3.x on Dataproc + BigQuery Scripted SQL (reconciliation)"]
        S2["💾 Storage<br/>GCS (staging Parquet) + BigQuery (target + audit_log)"]
        C2["📊 Consumption<br/>Consumption"]
